<HEADLINE> Mexican President Begins Visit to Uruguay </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
During his visit, the Mexican president will talk with his
counterpart Julio M. Sanguinetti and sign some cooperation
agreements with Uruguay.
</P>
<P>
Official sources said that Zedillo's visit may help unlock the
now stalled negotiations between Mexico and the Mercosur group,
which is made up of Argentina, Brazil, Paraguay and Uruguay.
