<HEADLINE> Myanmar Newspaper Urges More Interchanges With China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YANGON, July 1 (Xinhua) -- The official newspaper New Light of
Myanmar Thursday said that the peoples of Myanmar and China will
enjoy fruits of interchanges through the promotion of economic
cooperation between the two nations.
</P>
