In its editorial titled "Enhancing Bilateral Economic
Cooperation", the newspaper quoted Lieutenant-General Khin Nyunt,
first secretary of the Myanmar State Peace and Development Council
(SPDC), as saying that he had "successful" discussions with
Chinese leaders during his recent visit to Beijing.
