At the recent third coordination meeting of Myanmar's Leading
Committee for the Promotion of Economic Cooperation Between
Myanmar and China, Khin Nyunt also said that he had cordial
discussions with the Chinese leaders on the implementation of
tasks under the bilateral economic cooperation programs.
</P>
