China's Zhejiang Province, from October 8-12.
</P>
<P>
At a press conference held here Wednesday, a local governmental
official said that about 800 Chinese and foreign companies and
wholesale and retail dealers in the fashion, food, light industry,
and department store sector are expected to display their products
during the fair, the fifth of its kind.
</P>
