<HEADLINE> Novotna Crashes Out at Wimbledon Tennis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, July 1 (Xinhua) -- Defending women's champion Jana
Novotna of the Czech Republic crashed out of the Wimbledon
quarterfinals with a 6-3, 6-4 loss to third seed American Lindsay
Davenport on Thursday
</P>
