<HEADLINE> Newspaper Editorial on Chinese Communist Party Anniversary (4) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The editorial goes on to emphasize that political awareness is
at the core of the education drive.
</P>
<P>
"The politics that we are talking about is concrete and pure,"
it says.
</P>
<P>
It goes on to elaborate that political awareness refers to "
