communists are outstanding individuals who are armed with the most
advanced achievements of human civilization."
</P>
<P>
Noting that today's international competition means there will
be constant tests for the leadership of all countries in terms of
governmental skills and capabilities, the editorial says that
China's Communist Party members have a duty to work harder to make
the Party and the country stronger and more powerful. 
