terms of following the path of socialism," "falling down in their
political qualifications and beliefs," and "unable or partially
unable to adapt to the new situation to meet the demands of the
tasks ahead."
</P>
<P>
Indeed, it says, "Some of these officials have actually even
failed the new tests on their beliefs and dogma."
</P>
<P>
The editorial points out that in the new international
situation and scenario, the Party has to create various conditions
for future progress. It must also make painstaking efforts to
overcome many difficulties in order to lead the 1.2 billion
Chinese people positively forward in the ongoing reform and
opening up so as to realize and achieve the country's strategic
targets of national development.
</P>
<P>
It says that the most imperative thing to do at present is to
carry out and reinforce the existing results of the education
drive in theoretical study, political awareness and good conduct
and comprehensively strengthen the ideological, political and
organizational building of the Party. As a result, therefore, the
overall quality of the leadership and leaders at all levels will
be greatly improved.
</P>
<P>
Those government institutes that have already implemented and
carried out the education drive have proved that the CPC Central
Committee's decision on launching such a campaign is of great
strategic significance. It is an innovative process for enhancing
party building and an important measure in strengthening the
leadership, improving the quality of officials and resolving
outstanding problems in the spirit and style of work of the Party.
</P>
<P>
The editorial stresses that the education drive plays an
important role in increasing the cohesive force and capacity of
the CPC organizations at all levels and improving the political
awareness and the abilities and skills of the leaders.
</P>
