including one to Rinas Airport and a section on the Durres-Kukes
road, said the officer.
</P>
<P>
NATO forces "on humanitarian mission" began to operate in
Albania about two months ago and the contingent currently embraces
some 7,000 persons from NATO's 19-member countries, the ATA said.
