<HEADLINE> Mexico, Spain Sign Cooperation Agreements </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MEXICO CITY, June 30 (Xinhua) -- Mexico and Spain agreed
Wednesday to promote bilateral relations in the fields of
education and culture, said the Education Ministry.
</P>
